headline: Truist announces redemption of senior notes due October 2026
summary: Truist Financial Corporation (NYSE: TFC) today announced it will redeem all $750,000,000 principal amount outstanding of its fixed-to-floating rate senior notes due October 28, 2026 (CUSIP 89788MAJ1) on the redemption date of October 28, 2025.
